---
import { ChevronDown } from 'lucide-astro';
---

<section class="py-24 bg-white dark:bg-dark">
    <div class="max-w-3xl mx-auto px-6">
        <h2 class="text-3xl font-extrabold text-center mb-12 text-dark dark:text-white">Dudas Comunes</h2>
        <div class="space-y-4">
            <div class="border border-ice dark:border-slate-700 rounded-2xl bg-white dark:bg-slate-800 overflow-hidden">
                <button class="faq-btn w-full p-6 text-left flex justify-between items-center outline-none group">
                    <span class="font-bold text-dark dark:text-white group-hover:text-mint-500 transition-colors">¿Aceptan seguros médicos?</span>
                    <ChevronDown class="faq-icon transition-transform duration-300 dark:text-white" />
                </button>
                <div class="faq-content px-6 text-soft dark:text-mint-100/50">
                    Sí, trabajamos con las principales aseguradoras y prepagas. También ofrecemos planes de financiación directa.
                </div>
            </div>
            <div class="border border-ice dark:border-slate-700 rounded-2xl bg-white dark:bg-slate-800 overflow-hidden">
                <button class="faq-btn w-full p-6 text-left flex justify-between items-center outline-none group">
                    <span class="font-bold text-dark dark:text-white group-hover:text-mint-500 transition-colors">¿Duele el blanqueamiento dental?</span>
                    <ChevronDown class="faq-icon transition-transform duration-300 dark:text-white" />
                </button>
                <div class="faq-content px-6 text-soft dark:text-mint-100/50">
                    Nuestras técnicas láser con geles desensibilizantes aseguran una experiencia libre de dolor en el 99% de los casos.
                </div>
            </div>
        </div>
    </div>
</section>

<script>
    document.querySelectorAll('.faq-btn').forEach(btn => {
        btn.addEventListener('click', () => {
            const content = btn.nextElementSibling;
            const icon = btn.querySelector('.faq-icon');
            if (content instanceof HTMLElement && icon instanceof HTMLElement) {
                content.classList.toggle('active');
                icon.style.transform = content.classList.contains('active') ? 'rotate(180deg)' : 'rotate(0deg)';
            }
        });
    });
</script>
